    <name>TFCBM</name>
    <summary>The * Clipboard Manager - A powerful clipboard manager for GNOME</summary>

    <description>
        <p>
            TFCBM (The * Clipboard Manager) is a feature-rich clipboard manager
            designed for GNOME desktop environments. Keep track of your clipboard history,
            manage multiple items, and quickly access your copied content.
        </p>
        <p>Features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Track unlimited clipboard history</li>
            <li>Support for text, images, and files</li>
            <li>Quick search and filtering</li>
            <li>Tag and organize clipboard items</li>
            <li>Secure storage for sensitive data</li>
            <li>Keyboard shortcuts for quick access</li>
            <li>Beautiful GTK4/Libadwaita interface</li>
            <li>Optional GNOME Shell extension for seamless integration</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            The optional GNOME Shell extension provides system-wide clipboard monitoring
            and quick access through a keyboard shortcut (Ctrl+Escape by default).
        </p>
    </description>

